article_id:80,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Better Together's Ability "Hypnos's Bane" [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue where the Better Together wyrmprint ability &quot;Hypnos&#39;s Bane&quot; is not working against Hypnos&#39;s right claw in the Hypnos Showdown.</div><div>*This issue has been confirmed across all difficulty levels.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue.</div><div>Any further updates regarding this issue will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum<span class="local_date" data-local_date="1541493000"></span>]</strong></span><br>This issue was fixed in the data update at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1541487600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1541407500,update_time1542364309